nexcage (0.7.1-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Release v0.7.1 - libcrun ABI integration & stability fixes
  * libcrun ABI integration with FFI bindings
  * OCI state.json persistence with PID tracking
  * Robust kill command with multiple execution paths
  * Build compatibility fixes for Zig 0.15.1
  * Default network bridge changed to vmbr50
  * CNCF compliance improvements (DCO, SBOM, Provenance)
  * E2E test improvements (93% pass rate)
  * Input validation and security hardening
  * Optional libcrun/systemd linking for portability

 -- CageForge Team <contact@cageforge.com>  Fri, 31 Oct 2025 17:30:00 +0100

nexcage (0.7.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Release v0.7.0 - kill/state commands, Proxmox fixes, security hardening
  * OCI-compliant state command implementation
  * Kill command with SIGTERM/SIGKILL support
  * Proxmox-LXC driver improvements
  * Security input validation framework
  * Logger stability fixes
  * Debug logging gated by --debug flag
  * Path security validation for OCI bundles
  * ZFS pool and dataset validation

 -- CageForge Team <contact@cageforge.com>  Mon, 28 Oct 2025 12:00:00 +0100
